# Invoice Notes and Custom Fields (DodatkowyOpis in KSeF XML)
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_SECTION=Invoice Notes and Custom Fields
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_NOTE_MODE=Public Note Mode
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_NOTE_MODE_Help=Controls how the invoice public note is included in the KSeF XML.<br><b>Simple - Stopka</b> sends the note as plain text in the invoice footer (StopkaFaktury). This is the default.<br><b>Simple - Dodatkowy Opis</b> sends the full note as key-value entry with key "Uwagi", splitting into 256-character chunks if needed.<br><b>Key:Value - Dodatkowy Opis</b> parses each line at the first colon into separate key-value entries.<br><b>Disabled</b> omits the note from the KSeF XML entirely.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_NOTE_MODE_DISABLED=Disabled (note not included)
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_NOTE_MODE_SIMPLE=Simple (full note as remark)
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_NOTE_MODE_KEYVALUE=Key:Value (parse lines)
KSEF_NOTE_COMBINED_SIMPLE_STOPKA=Simple - Stopka Faktury (invoice footer as plain text)
KSEF_NOTE_COMBINED_SIMPLE_DODATKOWY=Simple - Dodatkowy Opis (additional description as "Uwagi" entry)
KSEF_NOTE_COMBINED_KEYVALUE_DODATKOWY=Key:Value - Dodatkowy Opis (parse note lines into key-value entries)
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_EXTRAFIELDS=Include Extrafields
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_EXTRAFIELDS_Help=Select which custom fields to include in the KSeF XML. Fields can target DodatkowyOpis (key-value pairs) or StopkaFaktury (invoice footer text). Both key and value are truncated to 256 characters.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_NO_EXTRAFIELDS=No custom extrafields available (only KSeF system fields found). Create extrafields in Dolibarr setup to use this feature.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_FACTURE_TITLE=Invoice Fields
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_FACTURE_SUBTITLE=Extrafields on the invoice card. Values you enter are included in KSeF XML as notes (label -> Klucz, value -> Wartosc). Choose where each field appears.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_FACTURE_NO_EXTRAFIELDS=No invoice extrafields available. Create invoice extrafields in Dolibarr setup or use the form below.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_DET_TITLE=Invoice Line Fields
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_DET_SUBTITLE=Extrafields on invoice line items. Values are included in KSeF XML as notes linked to the line via NrWiersza (label -> Klucz, value -> Wartosc). Always DodatkowyOpis.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_DET_NO_EXTRAFIELDS=No invoice line extrafields available. Create invoice line extrafields in Dolibarr setup or use the form below.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_PRODUCT_TITLE=Product Fields
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_PRODUCT_SUBTITLE=Extrafields on product/service cards. Values are included in KSeF XML as notes linked to the line via NrWiersza (label -> Klucz, value -> Wartosc). Always DodatkowyOpis.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_PRODUCT_NO_EXTRAFIELDS=No product extrafields available. Create product extrafields in Dolibarr setup or use the form below.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_SOCIETE_TITLE=Third Party Fields
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_SOCIETE_SUBTITLE=Extrafields on the third party card, sourced from the customer on each invoice. Values are included in KSeF XML as notes (label -> Klucz, value -> Wartosc). Choose where each field appears.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_SOCIETE_NO_EXTRAFIELDS=No third party extrafields available. Create third party extrafields in Dolibarr setup or use the form below.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_PROJECT_TITLE=Project Fields
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_PROJECT_SUBTITLE=Extrafields on the project card, sourced from the linked project. Values are included in KSeF XML as notes (label -> Klucz, value -> Wartosc). Choose where each field appears.
KSEF_DODATKOWY_OPIS_PROJECT_NO_EXTRAFIELDS=No project extrafields available. Create project extrafields in Dolibarr setup or use the form below.
