# Sending Invoices Section
KSEF_SendingInvoices=Sending Invoices
KSEF_UsingTheModule=Using the Module
KSEF_SubmitInvoice=Submit Invoice
KSEF_SubmittingInvoices=Submitting Invoices
KSEF_TheWorkflow=The Workflow
